product.title: Lambert - The Zoe Vegan Leather Case in Black
product.body_html: The essential travelling case for your long-haul and daily commutes. Made with premium, PETA-certified vegan leather, its compact shape and small interior pockets make it the ideal toiletry bag or travel kit. 22cm (length) x 18cm (height) x 9cm (width).
